10:19.183 --> 10:21.708
[Wind howling]

10:24.798 --> 10:26.538
[Bike chain clatters]

10:29.367 --> 10:31.543
You can finish that
in the car.

10:33.676 --> 10:36.287
[Thunder crashes]

